# express-jwt-mongodb-auth

A boilerplate project for building a secure user authentication API with Node.js, Express.js, JSON Web Tokens (JWT), and MongoDB. This project demonstrates best practices for user registration, login, and protected routes.

---

## Table of Contents

*   [English](#english)
    *   [Introduction](#introduction)
    *   [Features](#features)
    *   [Technologies Used](#technologies-used)
    *   [Prerequisites](#prerequisites)
